t and right.<br>　\"REC\" can also ride blocks!<br><br><strong>■Spiked block</strong><br>　Spiked block that fall from above<br>　Be careful not to get hit!<br><br><strong>■Falling floor</strong><br>　Some sections of the floors will fall when stepped on!<br><br><strong>■Spring floor</strong><br>　A one-time use bouncy floor that will send \"REC\" flying!<br><br><strong>■Number door</strong><br>　These doors can't be opened unless the correct number of blocks are placed on a switch.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/e02d9b74af9760ff0bc682263a736c3c.poster.avif?t=1770822141\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/e02d9b74af9760ff0bc682263a736c3c.webm?t=1770822141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/e02d9b74af9760ff0bc682263a736c3c.mp4?t=1770822141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Plus many more stage gimmicks to challenge you! <br>Guide \"REC\" through hundreds of puzzles to discover them all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/5412b1c85be4abbb5a6461344ea7c3ff.poster.avif?t=1770822141\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/5412b1c85be4abbb5a6461344ea7c3ff.webm?t=1770822141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608270/extras/5412b1c85be4abbb5a6461344ea7c3ff.mp4?t=1770822141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
